        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The NIRMAN SHRAMIK SIKSHA KAUSHAL VIKAS YOJANA (NSKKVY) is a scheme launched by the Government of Rajasthan to provide financial assistance for education and skill development to the children of registered construction workers in the state. Under the scheme, scholarships for education will be provided to the workers&#39; children. According to the scheme format, children studying from the 6th class to higher class (ITI, Diploma, Graduation, Post Graduation) can avail of the scheme&#39;s benefits by applying for the scholarship.\n",
        "benefits_md": "> **The following scholarships will be provided to the male and female students after taking admission in the upcoming class: -**\n\n<br>\n\nClassStudentStudent / Specially abledFrom class 6th to 8th₹ 8,000/- per year₹ 9,000/- per yearFrom class 9th to 12th₹ 9,000/- per year₹ 10,000/- per yearITI₹ 9,000/- per year₹ 10,000/- per yearDiploma₹ 10,000/- per year₹ 11,000/- per yearGraduation (General)₹ 13,000/- per year₹ 15,000/- per yearGraduate (Professional)₹ 18,000/- per year₹ 20,000/- per yearPost Graduate (General)₹15,000/- per year₹ 17,000/- per yearPost Graduate (Professional)₹ 23,000/- per year₹ 25,000/- per year<br>\n\n> **Beneficiary meritorious students will be given the following cash awards under the scheme:-**\n\n<br>\n\nClassPrize moneyClass 8th to 9th₹ 4,000/-class 11th₹ 6,000/-Diploma₹ 10,000/-Graduate₹ 8,000/-Postgraduate₹ 12,000/-Graduate (Professional)₹ 25,000/-Post Graduate (Professional)₹ 35,000/-<br>\n\n",
        "exclusions_md": "<br>\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "The NIRMAN SHRAMIK SIKSHA KAUSHAL VIKAS YOJANA (NSKKVY) is a scheme launched by the Government of Rajasthan to provide financial assistance for education and skill development to the children of registered construction workers in the state.",
        "detailedDescription": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The NIRMAN SHRAMIK SIKSHA KAUSHAL VIKAS YOJANA (NSKKVY) is a scheme launched by the Government of Rajasthan to provide financial assistance for education and skill development to the children of registered construction workers in the state. Under the scheme, scholarships for education will be provided to the workers' children. According to the scheme format, children studying from the 6th class to higher class (ITI, Diploma, Graduation, Post Graduation) can avail of the scheme's benefits by applying for the scholarship."
              }
